sequenceDiagram
    participant CS as Certstream (External)
    participant IG as Ingestor (Java)
    participant KF as Kafka Broker
    participant SP as Streams Processor (Java)
    participant AL as Alerter (Java)

    CS->>IG: New SSL Certificate Event (JSON)
    IG->>KF: Produce DomainEvent to 'raw-domains'
    KF->>SP: Consume Record
    Note over SP: Calculate Levenshtein Distance<br/>Check Similarity Threshold
    alt is Threat
        SP->>KF: Produce ThreatEvent to 'detected-threats'
        KF->>AL: Consume Threat
        AL->>AL: Save to PostgreSQL
        AL->>AL: Trigger Slack Notification
    else is Safe
        Note over SP: Drop Event
    end